Dr Clemenza is genuinely one of the worst professors I have had. She is super unclear when she explains concepts in lecture and expects you to remember small details in tutorial. This class is nothing like IMM250, way more complex and a lot more memorization. Lecture slides are never completed within the time allotted and the tutorials aren't very helpful. Test questions are very specific and require memorization of details.

She is not very articulate to teach a course that requires attention to detail. It is nothing like IMM250. Adding to that, she never completes all the slides with the time allotted. She is a literal beauty. Amazing 10/10 recommend.
